.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, electronic, blues, reggae
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, snowboarding, handball, sailing
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the fan of reggae is the person who's sport is handball##1
3. the fan of reggae is on the far right##1
4. the fan of electronic is the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the fan of blues is between the fan of house and the fan of electronic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | electronic     | blues           | house | reggae  |
| Sport         | golf | sailing | snowboarding   | handball |

