.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, blues, techno, rock
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike, skateboard, scooter
1. the fan of blues is the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the fan of pop##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
5. the fan of pop is between the person driving the trike and the fan of techno##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | rock   | blues | pop | techno      |
| Transport     | skateboard | trike    | quad-bike  | scooter |

