.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, climbing, ice-hockey, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, train, bike, bus
1. the person driving the scooter is the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person driving the bike##2
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Sport       | water-polo | golf | ice-hockey     | climbing   |
| Transport   | bike   | train     | bus | scooter |

