The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, roller, quad-bike, tram
1. the designer is between the person driving the jet-ski and the bartender##2
2. the person driving the tram is on the left of the bartender##1
3. the fisherman is on the right of the bartender##1
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
5. the bartender is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | project-manager | designer | bartender | fisherman |
| Transport   | jet-ski         | tram       | roller    | quad-bike         |

