.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: onion, apricot, papaya, radish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, basketball, climbing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
3. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person eating apricot and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food    | radish   | papaya      | apricot   | onion  |
| Sport   | rowing | basketball | climbing | handball |

