.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, pomegranate, cherry, artichoke
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, adventure, epic, musical
1. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is between the person eating artichoke and the person eating avocado##2
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person eating avocado##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Food          | avocado     | pomegranate | artichoke   | cherry        |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | epic   | adventure | musical |

