.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, video-games, card-games, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, ambient, electronic, house
1. the fan of electronic is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of jazz is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is the fan of ambient##1
5. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the fan of ambient is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | video-games | card-games | magic-tricks | woodworking |
| Music-Genre   | electronic          | ambient     | house  | jazz     |

