.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, nigerian, russian, spanish
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, taxi, airplane
1. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the spanish is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the russian is between the person driving the taxi and the nigerian##2
4. the spanish is on the right of the russian##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |   3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | russian | spanish |
| Transport     | helicopter     | motorbike   | airplane | taxi  |

