.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, german, canadian, colombian
4 different pets are kept: fish, snake, chinchilla, guinea-pig
1. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the colombian is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the fish and the german##2
4. the owner of the guinea-pig is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | colombian | german | mexican | canadian |
| Pet           | chinchilla  | guinea-pig  | snake | fish      |

