4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person driving the car##1
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby       | dancing | skydiving | photography | chess |
| Transport   | car    | snowmobile  | train    | taxi       |

