2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the french is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is between the indian and the nigerian##2
5. the nigerian is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | french   | indian   | russian | nigerian |
| Sport         | lacrosse | badminton | cycling     | swimming    |

