.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, board-games, magic-tricks, filmmaking
4 different pets are kept: horse, fish, turtle, pony
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the owner of the horse and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks    | filmmaking     | rock-climbing | board-games |
| Pet     | fish | pony | turtle       | horse     |

 